  "html": "<h2 class=\"\" id=\"overview-of-the-week\">Overview of the Week</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Went camping at Lake George with Ben, John, his new wife Kaitlyn, and Ben's parents Rachel and Garrett.</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<p class=\"\"></p><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Article about New York converting a closed prison into 1,300 homes, with calculations showing 260 affordable homes and 75 affordable apartments in initial phase.\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1719279562/Screenshot_2024-06-24_at_9.39.09_PM.png\" alt=\"Article about New York converting a closed prison into 1,300 homes, with calculations showing 260 affordable homes and 75 affordable apartments in initial phase.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1719279562/Screenshot_2024-06-24_at_9.39.09_PM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1719279562/Screenshot_2024-06-24_at_9.39.09_PM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1719279562/Screenshot_2024-06-24_at_9.39.09_PM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1719279562/Screenshot_2024-06-24_at_9.39.09_PM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Article about New York converting a closed prison into 1,300 homes, with calculations showing 260 affordable homes and 75 affordable apartments in initial phase.\" style=\"background-color:#222222;background-image:url(&#x22;data:image/jpeg;base64,&#x22;);background-size:cover;background-position:center;--splay-rot:-0.6deg;\" width=\"772\" height=\"1722\" data-dimensions=\"772×1722\" class=\"img-fu